programme.title: Jangan Benci Cintaku S1 Ep01
programme.desc: Rofeeka Huda (Feka) dan Shahrizal (Shah) telah disatukan direstui oleh kedua belah pihak ibu bapa mentuanya. Nek Pah menentang perkahwinan merek. Bagi Nek Pah, Feka langsung tidak memenuhi ciri-ciri isteri yang solehah. Feka mahu menikmati hidupnya terlebih dahulu, bersantai. Shah seorang suami yang penyabar dan tidak pernah mendesak Feka. . Tingkahlaku Feka kadangkala membuatkan Shah menyirap juga. Setiap hari, Shah akan bangun dulu sebelum Fika. Dalam pada itu, rakan baik Feka dan Damia iaitu Irwan masih berhubung dengan mereka, khususnya Feka. Irwan sebenarnya mencintai Feka. Tetapi bagi Irwan dia berpegang akan terus berkawan. Tanpa pengetahuan ibu dan bapa Feka, juga Shah, Feka dan Damia merancang untuk melanjutkan pengajian. Mereka dapat Universiti di Perth, Australia. Ibu dan bapa Feka tidak setuju. Manakala Shah hatinya begitu, tetapi menyatakan bersetuju hanya semata-mata mahu mengambil hatinya.

programme.title: Bib S1 Ep17
programme.desc: Affan mula mencari punca keluarganya makin rapuh. Syamil berprasangka buruk terhadap Dian dan kondo mewah yang didiaminya. Syamil taksub dengan Dian sehingga sanggup mengekori Dian sehingga ke rumah Dian.

programme.title: Masuk Jawi
programme.desc: Majlis berkhatan untuk tiga orang budak lelaki di sebuah kampung di negeri bahagian utara tanah air. Ibu bapa masing-masing telah berpakat untuk mengadakan majlis tersebut secara besar-besaran di rumah Tok Penghulu. Sebelum ini, majlis serupa mengalami kegagalan sebanyak empat kali, kerana ketiga-tiga mereka telah menggunakan pelbagai helah untuk melepaskan diri daripada Tok Mudim.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir S1 Ep16
programme.desc: Suzan kecewa dan anggap Aidid saja rahsiakan hal itu. Sh Kamariah bawa Suzan balik KL untuk selesaikan masalah ni. Tapi demi jaga aib Haryati, Aidid teruskan nikah. Haryati dan Juliana ambil kesempatan saiko Suzan supaya dia tarik diri dan tinggal Aidid. Suzan juga ugut Aidid, dia akan balik Izmir jika Aidid tak tunai janji untuk cerai Juliana lepas nikah nanti. Mujur Sh Kamariah ada jaga Suzan. Dan bila dia dapati Juliana adalah anak Sherry, Sh Kamariah faham yang Aidid adalah mangsa. Di hari pernikahan, Aidid nampak serba-salah nak teruskan majlis nikah atau tak.

programme.title: Jangan Benci Cintaku S1 Ep08
programme.desc: Feka yang pengsan sebenarnya dia juga mengalami tekanan darah tinggi. Lantaran itu, Shah meminta Faris menemani Feka ke Klinik, balik dari Klinik mereka berbual sambil minum. Semasa inilah Feka diberitahu punca dan bagaimana Shah mengenali Husna hingga kini bercinta. Ketika Feka ke klinik, Faris juga memaklumkan Shah balik bertemu neneknya. Shah menemui Neneknya (Nek Pa), Shah dinasihati oleh bapanya supaya jangan mudah berpoligami. Ketika di rumah, mereka tidak bergaduh sangat tetapi yang jelas antara mereka dingin. Feka kali ini menyatakan di saat ini Shah samada memilih Husna atau terus dengannya.

programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Kedua-dua Delisha dan Faiq melalui detik-detik kesusahan dan cabaran hidup. Mereka terpaksa membeli baju murah, tidur di hotel bajet, makan di warung. Sekarang, Faiq semakin tahu erti kesusahan, isterinya masih ada perasaan ego. Dia terus berlagak seperti orang berkemampuan. Dari jauh Delisha ternampak Zainal bersama Salima, Delisha ingin mendapatkan mereka, mungkin mereka tahu di mana Nendanya tetapi tidak disetujui Faiq. Dari situ mereka ke pejabat Nendanya, tiba di sana pejabat itu bukan lagi milik Nendanya dan mereka juga tidak dilayan di situ. Manakala Salima telah pun selesai majlis pertunangan mereka. Sikap Zainal yang terus berada di rumah Salima, membuatkan ibu Salima terpaksa berterus terang meminta Zainal pulang dahulu. Tingkah laku Zainal tidak sukai dan disenangi ibu Salima. Dalam pada itu, Salima terus dengan ego dan kerap bersama Zainal ke butik untuk mempersiapkan perkahwinan mereka.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Sekembalinya ke Malaysia, Zafuan maklumkan Juliana dahpun jadi tunang Aidid. Tapi Aidid rahsiakan dari Suzan. Dia bawa Suzan jumpa Haryati untuk terus-terang yang mereka dah bernikah. Tapi Suzan dikejutkan kenyataan pertunangan Aidid dan Juliana. Haryati juga takkan maafkan dia gara-gara babanya. Haryati ugut Aidid nikah juga dengan Juliana, jika tak Aidid akan disingkirkan dari jawatan CEO. Malah Haryati dan Juliana turut jumpa Suzan dan hina dia sebagai perampas dan ambil kesempatan atas kedudukan Aidid. Akhirnya Aidid tak tahan lalu ambil keputusan letak jawatan.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Aidid bawa Suzan balik rumah keluarga Sy Kamarudin untuk mula hidup baru. Aidid nak buka café konsep taman. Tok Ayah dan Tok Umi seronok terima mereka. Tapi tidak Sh Kamariah. Dia masih dingin walaupun Aidid cuba bantu dia cari bisnes baru. Sh Kamariah buat hal nak sakitkan hati Suzan. Tapi akhirnya dia sedar yang Suzan ikhlas dengan keluarganya. Haryati pula hadapi masalah bila kebanyakan pelanggan hanya mahu berurusan dengan Aidid. Apalagi bila Zafuan juga hantar notis berhenti kerja. Akhirnya Haryati hubungi Aidid minta dia balik KL. Aidid kembali dilema.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Suzan minta Aidid balik KL, biar dia tunggu di kampung. Haryati pula pujuk Aidid terus jadi CEO dan nikah dengan Juliana. Dia janji, Aidid bebas buat apapun lepas nikah termasuklah ceraikan Juliana. Haryati cuma nak jaga air mukanya saja. Aidid terpaksa setuju dan Haryati kembali ligat buat persiapan kawin. Zafuan nampak tak senang lalu nasihatkan Aidid supaya terus-terang dengan Suzan. Tapi Haryati rancang yang lebih jahat bila dia sengaja hantar kad undangan kahwin Aidid-Juliana ke email Sy Kamariah. Sy Kamariah terpaksa maklumkan Suzan. Suzan terkejut besar.

programme.desc: Shah cuba pujuk Feka supaya menyambung pengajiannya di Kuala Lumpur sahaja. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep07
programme.desc: Memaparkan Mizan keluar rumah meninggalkan Sheila dan ibu bapanya. Hani ketika berada di rumah Yusri/Sarah dihubungi ibu mentuanya meminta dia pulang. Sebelum itu, Khalid berharap Mizan membantunya untuk mendekati wanita idamannya. Mengikut Khalid wanita itu begitu sempurna sukar ditemui. Hani bergegas pulang dan di hadapan rumah dia ternampak dan dengar Suria sedang merayu dan memujuk Mizan, sedangkan Mizan marah serta meminta dia beredar. Di situlah Hani diperkenalkan Mizan sebagai isterinya, lantas Suria beredar. Hani meminta kebenaran Mizan untuk pulang ke kampung dan tidak disetujui Mizan keranai bimbang adiknya Nizam begitu mencintai Hani. Mizan salah faham permintaan ibunya agar Hani pulang untuk membantu Sheila. Mizan juga tidak tahu Nizam telah keluar rumah. Mizan sebenarnya salah sangka akhirnya membenarkan Hani dan dia juga semakin menyayangi Hani, tetapi memendamkannya. Semasa Hani menjaga Sheila di wad, Sheila mencerca Hani sebagai cuba merampas suaminya, cuba menunjuk baik kepada mentua dan berbagai-bagai. Sheila tidak menyukai Hani membantunya. Susulan itu, Hani tenang dan sabar kerana dia diamanah ibu dan bapa mentuanya. Hani juga menghubungi Nizam merayu pulang mendampingi Sheila, Nizam sebenarnya ke Langkawi dan bertegas tidak menyukai Sheila dan tidak akan pulang, malahan sanggup berbual semata-mata kerana Hani.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep08
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani menemani Sheila yang sakit hendak bersalin. Sheila memarahi dan meminta Hani tidak perlu menemainya. Hani sabar, tenang sebaliknya memaklumkan dia berbuat demikian atas kehendak ibu dan bapa mertua mereka. Setelah Hani menasihatinya dan meminta Sheila banyak istigfar dan berdoa daripada mengeluh dan ingat yang bukan-bukan, Sheila akhirnya berubah positif terhadap Hani. Nizam yang dihubungi Hani tidak menjawab. Sheila selamat melahirkan anaknya dan dia kekurangan darah dan Hani telah mendermanya. Mizan pula dimaklumkan Khalid tentang wanita idamannya tidak kelihatan beberapa hari. Jadi rancangan untuk menemuinya ditangguhkan dahulu. Sebelum itu Khalid juga bertanyakan Yusri tentang Hani tetapi Yusri juga tidak ketahui. Hani yang menjagai adik iparnya juga membantu ibu mentuanya di rumah. Dia keletihan dan ibunya meminta dia berehat dan tidur awal. Mizan pula mengutamakan ke kampungnya daripada majlis jemputan tetapi tiba lewat malam, Hani telah nyenyak tidur. Sheila berkali-kali menghantar pesanan ringkas kepada Nizam tetapi tiada sebarang jawapan. Dia juga teringat kisah lalu bagaimana bekas rakan lelakinya yang tidak mahu bertanggungjawab dan kemudiannya bertemu dengan Nizam.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep07
programme.desc: Memaparkan hubungan Melissa dengan Syakir baik sebagai suami isteri cuma mereka tidak tidur di bilik yang sama. Bukanlah akibat sesuatu tetapi Melissa sendiri masih kekok, dia masih memanggil tuan Syak kepada suaminya. Dia berbahasa begitu kerana Syakir adalah bosnya ketika bekerja di book cafe. Melissa berat untuk meninggalkan pekerjaannya tetapi atas permintaan suaminya dia sanggup berbuat begitu. Jenny majikannya pun agak berat untuk melepaskan tetapi kerana permintaan Syakir, dia tiada pilihan. Syakir membawa Melissa ke rumah baru. Melissa terkejut kerana rumah barunya ini lebih besar dan memerlukan tenaga kerja yang lebih. Atas sebab itu Syakir meminta Melissa untuk berhenti kerja dan menumpukan sepenuh perhatian sebagai suri rumah tangga. Mereka sentiasa bersama mengemas rumah, Syakir kelihatan puas hati tindak tanduk Melissa. Pelbagai kejadian lucu dan romantik yang berlaku sepanjang mereka berada di rumah tersebut. Syakir dan Melissa belajar untuk mengenali diri masing-masing di rumah tersebut kerana banyak masa yang mereka habiskan bersama. Suatu hari mereka ke pasaraya, di suatu ketika Syakir tertinggal satu barang di kaunter, ketika Melissa berdiri berseorangan Zamer ternampaknya dari jauh, dia cuba untuk ke situ, tiba-tiba datang Syakir semula dan mereka berjalan sama. Ini telah menghairankan Zamer dengan merungut Melissa masih bersama lelaki yang sama. Sementara itu Shamsul yang berbincang dengan Syakir tentang projek perniagaan bapanya yang mana dia kini perlu mengetua di bahagian akitek dalam satu projek baru. Di suatu ketika ibu Melissa tidak sihat, Melissa meminta izin balik menemui ibunya. Melissa tahu suaminya sibuk bekerja dan dia hanya memadai Syakir hantar ke stesen bas. Tiba di kampung Melissa jadi takut untuk menghubungi Syakir membuatkan Syakir tertunggu, bimbang dan sebagainya. Shamsul datang bersantai di bilik Syakir dan dia mendapati Syakir tidak bersemangat. Syakir akui dia terasa bosan pun ada, duduk rumah tidak kena dan duduk di pejabat pun tidak kena. Dari cerita Syakir Shamsul merujuk kepada pengalaman sama dia pernah lalui ketika dia berpisah 2 bulan dengan Nora. Jadi terasa amat sangat api cinta itu. Syakir terdiam, apabila jikanya sebegitu Syakir ditanyakan dia rindukan kepada siapa. Cakap-cakap Shamsul terbawa-bawa Syakir semasa berseorangan di rumahnya. Melissa bercadang akan menghubungi suaminya, tiba-tiba pintu rumahnya diketuk dan Melissa hairan seseorang yang datang itu

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep08
programme.desc: Memaparkan agak tergamam Melissa yang tiba itu suaminya. Melissa susah hati rumah mereka hanya ada dua bilik, sebilik telah dihuni ibunya dan sebilik lagi Syakir minta dia berehat, sedangkan bilik itu khas untuknya. Syakir menerangkan tidak apa apa masalah mereka tinggal sebilik tetapi Melissa setuju yang dia akan tidur di bawah katil dengan alasan darjat suami perlu di jaga. Syakir tidak peduli dan bila balik ke Kuala Lumpur hendak tidur bersama pun boleh dan tidur berasingan pun ada bilik yang banyak. Di pejabat bapa Syakir bertanyakan tentang prestasi kerja Syakir kepada Shamsul. Shamsul mendapati kerjakerjanya semua selesai dan bapanya juga kelihatan dia sentiasa ceria dan kreatif dengan kerjanya. Cuma yang menghairankan Shamsul pun tidak tahu dia kemana kerana dia bercuti seminggu lagi. Bapanya menanyakan adakah Syakir sedang bercinta, Shamsul juga tidak tahu. Bapanya meminta agar Shamsul memantau adiknya itu, bimbang terjadi sesuatu kerana akhir-akhir ini dia banyak berahsia. Takut apa yang terjadi ibunya nanti buat kacau yang bukan-bukan pula. Shamsul hanya mengiakan. Semasa di rumah ibu Melissa, Melissa bersapa dengan "abang" sebagai tidak meragukan ibunya. Syakir dan Melissa saling merindui walaupun masing-masing tidak mahu mengakuinya. Walaupun sudah sah menjadi suami isteri, Melissa masih lagi menjaga auratnya di hadapan Syakir. Manakala di rumah Kamelia dia mendesak abangnya ingin tahu lokasi Syakir, sedangkan abangnya marah sikapnya opses masih mengejar Syakir. Sementara itu Nora, kakak ipar Syakir berada di wad kerana keguguran. Syakir yang dapat tahu berjanji akan balik ke Kuala Lumpur. Shamsul sebenarnya berkawan baik dengan Engku Razi, dia berkongsi masalah yang dihadapi dan Engku Razi simpati. Engku Razi memberitahu hal Nora kepada Engku kamelia. Engku Kamelia tidak kisah, apa yang mahu hanya Syakir bukan keluarga mereka. Melissa dan Syakir kini balik di rumah mereka, kemesraan semakin baik, tetapi Melissa masih takut-takut dan Syakir meminta Melissa jangan memanggilnya sebagai tuan Syak. Melissa juga memaklumkan ada surat untuk Syakir diterima. Dalam pada itu Zamer pula memandu membawa Engku Kamelia. Kamelia masuk ke dalam book cafe dan meminta Zamer jawab panggilan dan memegang sebentar tas tangannya. Semasa inilah ada panggilan daripada Syakir, Zamer tidak menjawab tetapi dia tertanya sendiri apakah pula hubungan Syakir ini dengan Kamelia

programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Kedua-dua Delisha dan Faiq melalui detik-detik kesusahan dan cabaran hidup. Mereka terpaksa membeli baju murah, tidur di hotel bajet, makan di warung. Sekarang, Faiq semakin tahu erti kesusahan, isterinya masih ada perasaan ego. Dia terus berlagak seperti orang berkemampuan. Dari jauh Delisha ternampak Zainal bersama Salima, Delisha ingin mendapatkan mereka, mungkin mereka tahu di mana Nendanya tetapi tidak disetujui Faiq. Dari situ mereka ke pejabat Nendanya, tiba di sana pejabat itu bukan lagi milik Nendanya dan mereka juga tidak dilayan di situ. Manakala Salima telah pun selesai majlis pertunangan mereka. Sikap Zainal yang terus berada di rumah Salima, membuatkan ibu Salima terpaksa berterus terang meminta Zainal pulang dahulu. Tingkah laku Zainal tidak sukai dan disenangi ibu Salima. Dalam pada itu, Salima terus dengan ego dan kerap bersama Zainal ke butik untuk mempersiapkan perkahwinan mereka.

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna 2 Ep22
programme.desc: Zalia beritahu Zahir yang dia tahu ini semua rancangan Zahir dan dia akan pastikan yang Zahir takkan terlepas. Hakimi tiba – tiba muncul semula. Hakimi culik Fariesya sebab dia tahu yang Fariesya bersubahat dengan Zahir untuk bunuhnya. Fariesya pujuk Hakimi untuk bunuh Zalia tapi Hakimi tak boleh buat semua tu. Dia terhutang budi dengan Zalia dan Zahid.

programme.title: Gila Baby
programme.desc: Bob memerlukan wang yang banyak bagi membiayai kos pembedahan ayahnya di hospital. Dengan mengambil jalan mudah, Bob membantu Roy, bekas teman sekelasnya di sekolah yang selalu membulinya dahulu untuk melakukan jenayah mencuri kereta. Walaupun percubaan pertama Bob untuk aktiviti jenayah tersebut berjaya tetapi ada seorang bayi di tempat duduk belakang kereta yang dicurinya itu! Bob kini mendapati dirinya diburu oleh beberapa pihak yang tidak akan berhenti selagi Bob dan bayi tersebut tidak ditangkap! Untuk mengeruhkan lagi keadaan, dalam perjalanan menyelamatkan diri, Bob bertemu Jaja yang mengugut Bob untuk membawanya sekali kerana ingin lari dari masalahnya sendiri

programme.title: Sesat
programme.desc: Ditinggalkan oleh bapanya, Amara dan keluarganya berpindah ke sebuah kampung. Ia kemudiannya mendapati bahawa kampung itu mempunyai masa lalu yang mencengkam. Penduduknya digeruni oleh sesuatu yang ghaib. Namun, sudah terlambat untuk Amara tahu. Gadis ini melakukan sesuatu yang tidak dijangka dan membahayakan nyawa orang tersayang.

programme.title: Japanizi Going Going Gong S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Empat pasukan dewasa dan kanak-kanak membuktikan mereka bukan ayam semasa Frenzy, dan mereka boleh menghidangkan teh buih dalam keadaan licin. Tetapi bolehkah mereka mengelak daripada tenggelam?

programme.title: Pocong The Origin
programme.desc: Pocong the Origin mengisahkan tentang seorang gadis muda bernama Sasthi, lakonan Nadya Arina. Semasa kecil, Sasthi menjalani hari-harinya dengan penuh tekanan dan penghinaan daripada orang sekeliling kerana dia dianggap sebagai keturunan pengikut ilmu hitam.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Kisah bermula pada satu malam apabila SARAKIT mengalami mimpi yang menakutkan. Dalam mimpinya itu, satu LEMBAGA PEREMPUAN yang berlumuran dengan darah muncul di hadapan SARAKIT sambil meminta tolong. SARAKIT menghampiri LEMBAGA tersebut. Tiba-tiba LEMBAGA itu bertukar wajah menjadi perempuan yang berwajah hodoh dan menakutkan. LEMBAGA itu mengejar SARAKIT. SARAKIT tersedar dari tidurnya apabila dia dikejutkan oleh RAFIQ. Dalam waktu yang sama, bomoh yang diupah oleh PN MARIAM sedang berusaha untuk memisahkan antara SARAKIT dengan RAFIQ. Bomoh itu berpuas hati setelah usahanya selesai.

programme.title: Si Jantung Hati
programme.desc: Dua adik beradik, Do dan Re, keluar menggembara untuk mencari harta pusaka kepunyaan ayah mereka yang telah lama disembunyikan. Tetapi sesuatu terjadi apabila musuh lama muncul kembali untuk mengambil harta pusaka itu kerana yakin bahawa itu miliknya yang telah dicuri ayah mereka bertahun-tahun dahulu.

programme.title: Jejaka Perasan
programme.desc: Dolah dan Dolit, masing-masing telah dihalau dari rumah oleh ibu dan isteri kerana malas bekerja dan gemar bermain judi kuda. Mereka pun menyewa bilik di rumah Pak Wok. Pak Wok tinggal bersama anaknya Rizan yang sedang bercinta dengan Amir. Mereka ditawarkan bekerja sebagai tukang cuci oleh Dato Kamarul kerana telah membantu membaiki kereta anaknya, Dora. Mulalah tersebar cerita bahawa mereka merupakan pegawai tetapi sebenarnya tidak.

programme.title: Pak Tam Duda
programme.desc: Dihormati oleh orang-orang kampung kerana baik-hati dan pemurah, Pak Tam ialah seorang duda dan usahawan yang berjaya di kampungnya. Niat jahat mereka telah dihidu budak-budak kampung yang tampil memberikan nasihat kepada Pak Tam.

programme.title: Penyamun Tarbus

programme.title: Hantu Siang
programme.desc: Seorang kasanova yang suka menggoda gadis menerima padahnya apabila harus mengahwini mangsanya. Badul telah berjaya mendampingi lebih 17 gadis. Dia mempunyai rancangan untuk menggoda dua lagi gadis baru sebagai mangsanya. Rancangan Badul memakan diri apabila dia sendiri terpaksa menikahi mereka - cubaannya telah memerangkap dirinya sendiri.

programme.title: Oh Fatimah
programme.desc: Perpisahan antara Rahmat dan Fatimah telah membawa keduanya untuk membina kehidupan baru bersama pasangan yang lebih baik. Kedua-duanya mula berkenalan dengan orang baru dan masing-masing cuba untuk menunjukkan betapa bagusnya pasangan baru mereka itu. Akan tetapi, sikap Rahmat yang mulai berubah telah mencairkan semula hati Fatimah - namun kesetiaan Rahmat perlu diuji dahulu sebelum Fatimah dapat membuat keputusan.

programme.title: Si Badol
programme.desc: Perjuangan kelas pekerja digambarkan apabila kapitalisme semakin mendapat tempat di dunia. Badol, seorang penipu, menyamar menjadi orang kaya yang datang dari Sarawak lalu mengahwini Milah. Tipu helah digunakannya untuk memperdaya orang kaya. Modus operandinya adalah dengan meminjam wang yang banyak. Badol pun pergi menghilangkan diri setelah berjaya memperdaya orang kaya.

programme.title: Pening Pening Lalat
programme.desc: Dino berjaya melarikan diri dari sebuah penjara dan sedang berada dalam buruan polis. Berita tentangnya mendapat liputan besar dan ditawarkan wang sebanyak RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang menangkapnya. Mengetahui tentang itu, Dino mula menyembunyikan diri. Memutuskan untuk bersembunyi di hutan, Dino bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.title: Tuan Badol
programme.desc: Seorang yang sangat garang tetapi rupa-rupanya takut dengan isteri, itulah Ibrahim. Seorang Pengurus Besar, dia mempunyai seorang pembantu rumah bernama Nor. Tuan Badol jatuh cinta terhadap Nor apabila melakukan lawatan ke tanah miliknya. Pelbagai cara telah dicubanya untuk memikat Nor, seorang yang hidup serba sederhana di tanah perkampungan setinggan miliknya.

programme.title: Bertunang
programme.desc: Darus ingin dikahwini dengan Zarinah, anak pengurus bank oleh bapa saudaranya - dia merupakan seorang yang kaya-raya. Namun, Darus melarikan diri kerana dia enggan mengahwini Zarinah dan sudah mempunyai kekasih hati. Mengetahui tujuan bapa saudaranya ingin menjodohkannya bersama anak seorang pengurus bank untuk membiayai projeknya, Darus hilang membawa diri - tetapi bapa saudaranya mempunyai rancangannya yang tersendiri.

programme.title: Senja Merah
programme.desc: Mahmud, seorang taikun yang berkahwin dengan seorang janda yang mempunyai seorang anak lelaki, Zubaidah adalah pengusaha restoran. Baharum, anak kepada zubaidah berkawan dengan Mahmud anak angkat Mira sejak kecil. Apabila dewasa, hubungan mereka semakin kuat dan mereka saling menyayangi. programme.title: Bibik Kayangan

Saadon, Kiah dan Melah sudah lama menjadi pembantu rumah di banglo milik Datuk Syafik dan Datin Sally. programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep839840
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: Player in Kaohsiung (M) Ep3637
programme.desc:
The name “Kaohsiung” has entered into a century of history since it has been renamed from “Da Gou”. This year, the National Day fireworks will be held again in Kaohsiung after 20 years passed. SETI has specially produced a new travelogue for Kaohsiung, leading the audience to visit the most popular, charming, and unique places in Kaohsiung. Through the lens, the century-old glory of Kaohsiung’s [One-Hundred] is presented profoundly.
The new season of "Player in Kaohsiung" invites many hosts and celebrities, including Yao Yao, Chang Chin Lan, Daniel Chen, David Wu, Ada Chang, Fay Wu, and Kua Kua, visit the 38 administrative districts of Kaohsiung to explore the sensational stories of the people in the alleys, deeply explore the professional spirit of the Greater Kaohsiung area, the traditions and customs of the aboriginal people, the living beside the farms and ports, and the humanism nurtured by Kaohsiung’s century-old history.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep424
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Back To Home (M) Ep1819
programme.desc: When the news reached her that the old village leader had passed away, Xiao Li, who was a personal shopper, stuffed a few things into her Hermes bag and, clutching the lucky salt he had once given her, set out for her home town wearing her Prada high-heeled shoes. That night A-Jian, who was helping out in a Japanese restaurant, also jumped on the bus and headed home as soon as he received the news. In his will, the old man divided up his salt fields among the villagers, but on the condition that A-Jian and Xiao Li get married. When they heard this, A-Jian and Xiao Li found themselves immediately surrounded…

programme.desc: Journalist with an infallible nose for a story is leading the audience to explore the world. Exploring how people from different cultures overcome the challenges with collective wisdom.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep425
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Piggy's Counter-Attack (M) Ep5657
programme.desc: A rich father, who built his fortune from nothing, goes bankrupt overnight when his investments fail. His children are knocked out of heaven and have to launch a counterattack.

programme.title: Legally Declared Dead
programme.desc: Insurance agent Sean visits Tak and Ling's home to follow up on a case and is shocked to see their son's corpse hanging above him. He suspects them of murdering their son to claim the insurance money and decides to launch his own investigation. As he becomes obsessed over their guilt, his kind nature is used against him by the real perpetrator.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Still Human
programme.desc: Evelyn, a Filipino domestic helper, moves to Hong Kong to work for Cheong Wing, a divorcee paralyzed in a construction accident. Becoming unlikely friends, the two discover shared humanity that helps them face life’s mounting hardships.

programme.title: Behind the Yellow Line
programme.desc: A fresh graduate, Paul, strikes up an acquaintance with a pretty young girl, Monica, on the metro. Monica is involved in a love affair with a married man while Paul is also pursued by a rich girl. When Paul vows his true love for Monica, she suggests playing hide-and-seek with him in the metro to decide if they are fated to be together.

programme.title: Munitions Hijacking Case
programme.desc: Agent Wen is assigned to work undercover for a Southeast Asian military arm dealer to find some munitions and to destroy them. When he finally finds the munitions though, he is attacked by unknown gangsters and has to team up with his partner to recover the munitions so as to prevent a disaster from occurring.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: Triad
programme.desc: This is a story about the Hong Kong Triads. Ting (William Chan). Cheung (Derek Tsang) and Dong (Edward Chui) are childhood friends who join a Triad together. After joining however, they discover that fame and fortune will ultimately break them apart as only one of them can become the leader of the gang.

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score…

programme.title: Keep Rolling
programme.desc: Directorial debut of Man Lim Chung, who spent 3 years filming this documentary about the life and filmmaking philosophy of Ann Hui, one of Hong Kong’s greatest filmmakers. It traces Hui’s life story and her 40-year career’s ups and downs using film footages, candid conversations with Hui, and interviews with her collaborators, family and friends.

programme.title: Man on the Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Fallen Angels
programme.desc: The funkier cousin to Chungking Express, director Wong Kar Wai looks at five fallen angels who suffer love and loss amidst the crime and chaos of Hong Kong’s neon nights. Karen Mok won Best Supporting Actress in the 15th Hong Kong Film Awards for her remarkable role as a broken-hearted party girl.

programme.title: Fall in Love at First Kiss
programme.desc: In this romantic love story starring Taiwanese actors Darren Wang and Jelly Lin, an ordinary girl develops a stubborn crush on the school genius after an unexpected kiss. But with the genius adored by everyone in the school, can their relationship blossom and develop?

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: I Love Lolanto
programme.desc: Lolanto, a playboy, is injured and meets the daughter of a tycoon, Man, in the hospital. Man is mentally retarded and makes friends easily with Lolanto hence Man’s father hires him to take care of her. However, as Man goes through treatments and recovers, her feelings for Lolanto also changes…

programme.title: Kill Mobile
programme.desc: Seven friends get together and decide to play a game where they must share all the messages and calls and app notifications on each other’s cell phones. Hilarity and drama follows as everyone's secrets are unveiled throughout the evening, and the seven friends find themselves more like strangers to each other than ever before!

programme.title: Incredible Monk, Dragon Return, The
programme.desc: Ko Yan Kit is a famous General in Song dynasty. Due to public pressure, Ko dare not confess his feeling for his first love Fung Yee, who is forced to work in a brothel. Feeling helpless, he asks a monk for help. Everything goes smoothly, but when Fung Yee is suddenly killed, the monk must travel to the underworld to save Ko’s first love!

programme.title: That Demon Within
programme.desc: A dutiful police Dave, saves the life of a gang leader, Lin. When Lin commits another crime, Dave regrets his action and suffers from a severe mental disorder at the same time. He becomes a fugitive wanted for murder and tries to destroy Lin and his gang so as to restore his reputation as a good police officer.

programme.title: Hello Babies
programme.desc: Lui Ming and Yeung Wai are constantly fighting with each other on everything, and now they are competing to be the first to get a grandson. Lui hires the Super Star midwife Gong San to “supervise” their sons and nephews to make it happen…

programme.title: Chungking Express
programme.desc: Two Hong Kong urban love stories depicting two Hong Kong policemen, both jilted by ex-lovers and falling in love again. One falls for a mysterious female underworld figure while the other is in love with a beautiful and witty server at a fast food restaurant he frequents.

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Ru’s financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed. To protect the client’s data, the company brings in the police to investigate. In the meantime, an analyst disappears and the Technical Director resigns. Is there a bigger crisis lurking behind?

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Long’s daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity…

programme.title: Love is…Pyjamas
programme.desc: Underwear designer Spring and her daughter work at Hugo’s enterprise. Hugo demands a new fashion line design competition between Spring and the newly employed ex model Jojo to save his company from bankruptcy and the winner will take charge of the line. Who will win the competition and will Hugo’s enterprise be saved?

programme.title: Peace Breaker
programme.desc: Police officer Gao accidentally kills a pedestrian on the way to his mother's funeral. He tries to dispose the body by hiding it in his mother's coffin. As the pedestrian turns out to be a wanted person and a police officer witnessed the accident, Gao is forced to bring his body back to the police station. Can the case be settled so easily?

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s’ Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Rhapsody of Kidnapping
programme.desc: When three tech founders end up handing over their latest inventions to a sleazy tycoon who takes them for granted, they decide to kidnap the man’s wife, mistress, love child and his grandma for a huge ransom. Little did they expect that the heartless tycoon has hired an assassin to take them out instead of paying the ransom.

programme.title: Rise of the Legend
programme.desc: The young Wong Fei Hung is a fearless fighter who aligns himself with one of the two gang leaders ruling Guangzhou. However, there is more to the young Wong Fei Hung than meets the eye as he has a more dangerous agenda in mind.

programme.title: All U Need is Love
programme.desc: Ten major film companies join forces on a comedy-drama film to raise funds and create jobs for industry workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. This film features an all-star ensemble cast starring for free, with the story revolving around a group of hotel guests placed under quarantine in Hong Kong.

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack…

programme.title: Blind War
programme.desc: Former SWAT captain Dong Gu suffers traumatic visual loss during a failed mission for which he is forced to take responsibility. He manages to get over and adapt to the situation with his daughter’s company, until his nemesis appears and puts his daughter in danger. Despite being blind, Dong Gu must fight to save his daughter.

programme.title: Mr McDreamy
programme.desc: A second generation rich man squanders his parents’ money and calls himself Mr McDreamy. When his parents finally have enough and cut him off financially, he establishes a “Mr McDreamy Training Academy” using various unconventional means to transform his four recruits into “Mr McDreamies” with hilarious results.

programme.title: A Better Tomorrow 2018
programme.desc: In this remake of John Woo's legendary heroic bloodshed movie, a former drug smuggler attempts to start his life anew and repair his relationship with his estranged brother, who is a rising star in the Police Narcotics Division.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Choi’s actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: The Killer
programme.desc: Hsieh Choun, the Black Dragon, is in trouble with the police since Wang Sien Tien's gang is helping them; he is no longer free to conduct his drugs shipments out of the port freely as he used to. He buys more thugs and killers to dispose of the young upstart, and soon Wang is in dire straits, in the port of Hong Kong.

programme.title: That Man In Chang-An
programme.desc: The Han Emperor dies and his Empress Lu seizes the ruling power. She plots to kill the heir to the throne, Liu Heng, but the masked warrior discovers her plot and tips off Liu. Liu sends his princess to Chang An to ask for help. The masked warrior protects the princess from attackers along the way and supports Liu to become the new Emperor.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: The Black Butterfly
programme.desc: Kwan leads a double life as a waitress and as an infamous outlaw skilled in martial arts, The Black Butterfly. When she steals a cache of gold from the Five Devils Rock bandits, she soon has the bandits, and the government, on her tail.

programme.title: River Of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her. In an ensuing struggle to free her from his clutches, her husband dies in a car accident. Blamed by her father-in-law for her husband’s death, Fang gets chased out of the house and goes back to singing to make a living...

programme.title: Clan Of The White Lotus
programme.desc: The head of White Lotus Clan, Lo, is a highly skilled martial artist who supports the Qing government and helps destroy the rebellion group. Hung from Shaolin who kills Lo’s brother, is being hunted and hides in another rebel Hu’s house. The clan attacks at night killing Hu and his sister, but Hung manages to get Hu’s pregnant wife to safety.

programme.title: The Adulteress
programme.desc: The film is about the drugged, then disgraced wife of a peddler in the waning days of the Ching Dynasty. To make matters worse, she’s soon framed for her husband’s murder by her rapist, the son of the local magistrate! And even that is not the end of her woes in this emotional suspense…

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: The friendship of three men who are close as brothers is put through the ultimate test when one of them gives in to corruption and pursues his love for his friend's wife.

programme.title: Big Times For The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again…

programme.title: Portrait In Crystal
programme.desc: Tragic deaths in the underworld cause leader "Yama" (Teng Wei-hao) to suspect a portrait in crystal with mysterious powers. He sends Hen Pan (Chen Hung) and Pai Pan (Hung Hsin-nan) to interrogate its creator, martial artist Lung Fei (Pai Piao)...

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: The Land Of Many Perfumes
programme.desc: Monk Tang San Zang, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing find themselves in Womanland, where women give birth to baby girls by drinking the magical spring water.

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: A titular gang of misfits come together to protect a patriotic general from a scheming usurper. To this end, the unlikely heroes act as the general’s escorts on a dangerous journey to a distant British consulate, beset by enemies and sinister Japanese interference along the way.

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: Mulan disguises herself as a male soldier to replace her aged father in a war against the barbarians. Her courage brings her victory in battles and she was promoted to a general. When Mulan returns home with glory, the chief commander asks her to marry his daughter, forcing Mulan to reveal her true identity.

programme.title: The Thunderbolt Fist
programme.desc: A vicious Japanese judo expert wants to prove that Chinese are the “sick people of Asia” and sets out to sabotage and kill the best martial artists in dangerous tournaments. To save his son from this, the head of Ping Pai Boxing Institute sends him to the mountains to learn the powerful Thunderbolt Fist technique from master fighter, Red Butterfly.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: The Brave Archer 3
programme.desc: Guo Jing and Huang Rong go to Iron Palm Peak to search for the Book of Wumu. The chief of Iron Palm discovers their visit, and seriously injures Huang. It seems only the Southern Emperor Duan can heal her, but will Huang be healed in time?

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Flying Guillotine 2
programme.desc: In a time of anti-Manchu sentiment, Emperor Yong Zheng employs his ruthless Blood Hound Corps to silence any dissenters. Only one man and his signature weapon, The Flying Guillotine, stand in their way.

programme.title: Apartment For Ladies
programme.desc: A Taiwanese singer comes to Hong Kong in search for her missing younger sister, who had arrived in Hong Kong to be discovered as a nightclub singer. She finds lodging at an apartment for women run by a man-hating landlady, Mrs Chan. However, Mrs Chan cannot confine the young ladies’ youthful vitality within the apartment.

programme.title: Ambush
programme.desc: Constable Wen Chao Fan and his father are framed for a jewel robbery they did not commit. On the run from the law and becoming a wanted fugitive, Wen must recover the jewels in order to clear his family name, but unfortunately he is not the only one seeking the stolen jewels...

programme.title: Melody Of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s “a-go-go” era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: Ghosts Galore
programme.desc: Young Taoist priest Lu and his friend are nearly killed by a female ghost during an exorcism. Luckily, Master Lian saves their lives, so they beseech him to teach them his skills. When his friend is killed by ruthless ninjas, Lu decides to learn the ultimate witchcraft and teams up with his master to defeat them.

programme.title: Forbidden Tales Of Two Cities
programme.desc: Li Han-hsiang wrote and directed this charming and fascinating comedy, Forbidden Tales Of Two Cities. The two cities in the picture are Macau, where a love quartet is a morally-unsound source for sexual entertainment; and Hong Kong, where a woman enters a gambler’s apartment to find four shackles hanging from his ceiling to aid in kinky activities.

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical production showcases personable singer/actor George Lam, who tries to find love and success in the world of TV commercials along with his buddies Hamburger and Snoopy.

programme.title: The Happiest Moment
programme.desc: In this horror anthology an old man dies from an overdose of virility pills, a cop goes on the run after extorting money from a hooker, and a mortician's ghost goes on the rampage.

programme.title: Invincible Shaolin
programme.desc: An evil Qing general comes up with a plan to rid the Shaolin masters once and for all. He invites three Northern Shaolin experts to fight against three Southern Shaolin disciples. After the contest, the general secretly kills the Southerners and places the blame on the Northerners. This leads to in-fighting between both Shaolin schools.

programme.title: Lover'S Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a man’s role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: The seventh daughter of the Jade Emperor is banished from heaven to live a mortal life as she is very mischievous. She falls in love with a young village lad Yong, who sold himself to work for the rich so as to bury his father. The goddess sisters help Yong to pay his debt so the lovebirds can be together. Is this going to end happily-ever-after?

programme.title: The Fantastic Magic Baby
programme.desc: The story is about the legendary Monkey King (Liu Chung-chun) teams up with Goddess of Mercy (Chao Li-chuan) and the Dragon Girl (Lung Nu) to battle the child god Hung Hai-erh (Ting Hua-chung),son of the Ox Demon (Hung Hai-erh) to rescue Tang Tseng, the Holy Pilgrim (Teng Chio-jen).

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: The Golden Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman supreme Cheng Pei-pei (Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon) teams up with director/writer/actor Lo Wei (director of Bruce Lee and Jackie Chan’s first major movies) for an evocative and terrific “Martial arts world” adventure consisting of a missing blade and a deadly sect of men-hating swordswomen.

programme.title: The Butterfly Chalice
programme.desc: Starring the stunning, teenage heartthrob Pat Ting Hung, The Butterfly Chalice marks the important directing debut of the kung-fu film genre's most principle figure Chang Cheh, as he burst the martial arts and swordplay movie doors wide open, announcing the beginning of the end for the Cantonese musicals.

programme.title: The 36Th Chamber Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Gordon Liu plays an anti-Manchu rebel who escapes to the Shaolin Temple and learns what it truly takes to become a martial arts master by challenging the 35 Shaolin Kung Fu chambers, eventually creating the 36th chamber himself.

programme.title: Enai Noki Payum Thotta
programme.desc: Raghu, a normal college guy gets dragged into trouble when he falls in love with Lekha and their whirlwind romance changes the course of his life.

programme.title: Market Raja Mbbs
programme.desc: While in the pursuit of Raja, a ruthless don, the police accidentally kill Chandrababu, a medical student. Things take a turn when Chandrababu's spirit possesses Raja and turns him into a gentle soul.

programme.title: Idhu Ennoda Jilla
programme.desc: Veera loses his father in a village fight arising out of a long-standing rivalry. Can he avenge his father's death and put an end to the violence?

programme.title: Kaalidas
programme.desc: A cop, who suffers from family issues, takes up a peculiar suicide case. The plot thickens as similar cases get reported within a span of a few days.

programme.title: Mirchi Masala
programme.desc: A woman decides to fight against her powerful oppressor. When the guard of a chilli factory helps her, the women and the teacher of the village join them to openly defy the prevailing repression.

programme.title: Varappogum 24 Manikkul
programme.desc: Three fugitives barge into a couple's house while escaping the authorities. However, they are flummoxed after finding the wife concealing a murder that has transpired in her home.

programme.title: Iru Mugan
programme.desc: Love creates a new drug called Speed which was used by Hitler during WW2 to transform humans into superhumans. Agillan lost his wife and quits his job as RAW Agent.

programme.title: Karnan
programme.desc: Karnan, a fearless village youth, must fight for the rights of the conservative people of his village, due to the torture given by a police officer.

programme.title: Nerkonda Paarvai
programme.desc: When three young women are implicated in a crime, a retired lawyer steps forward to help them clear their names.

programme.title: Madhura Raja
programme.desc: Raja Narashima, a respected village head, tries to save his elder brother who is falsely implicated in a crime he did not commit. Things get difficult when he comes across an illegal liquor dealer.

programme.title: Ka Pe Ranasingam
programme.desc: The story is about politics surrounding land and the plight of farmers. It showed Vijay helping poor farmers in their fight against the industries that have acquired their lands.

programme.title: Magalir Mattum
programme.desc: Prabhavati, an independent documentary filmmaker, with the help of her friends takes her mother-in-law, Gomatha, on a surprise trip to reunite her with her school friends.

programme.title: Thondan
programme.desc: Narayanan, a politician's son, assaults Vishnu when his brother dies in his ambulance. Later, he makes Vishnu's life miserable by bribing the local police officers and government officials.

programme.title: Uri: The Surgical Strike
programme.desc: Indian army special forces execute a covert operation, avenging the killing of fellow army men at their base by a terrorist group.

programme.title: Wild Dog
programme.desc: A series of deadly attacks occur that pose a threat to national security. In response, a brash but brilliant intelligence agent leads a covert operation to find the perpetrators.

programme.title: Lakshmi
programme.desc: Lakshmi dreams of winning a national level dance competition but is scared to participate as her mother despises dancing. However, things take a turn when she meets Krishna, a cafe owner.

programme.title: Vikram Vedha
programme.desc: A tough police officer sets out to track down and kill an equally tough gangster.

programme.title: Yaman
programme.desc: After losing his father to a bunch of scheming politicians, a young man decides to wade into the corrupt and unscrupulous world of politics to avenge his death.

programme.title: Kanaa
programme.desc: A woman who hails from a middle-class family background aims to excel in the competitive world of cricket with the help of her supportive father.

programme.title: Rajini Murugan
programme.desc: An unemployed Rajini Murugan falls in love with Karthika, but her father opposes their union due to an old misunderstanding. Things get better after Rajini inherits his grandfather's property.

programme.title: Idhu Kadhirvelan Kadhal
programme.desc: Kathir, who hates marriage, is in Coimbatore to resolve a family dispute. There, he falls for Pavithra but his heart is broken when he discovers that she is in love with someone else.

programme.title: Irumbuthirai
programme.desc: A military officer borrows money from a bank using fake papers for his sister's marriage. However, when the money goes missing from his account, he begins an investigation that leads him to a hacker.

programme.title: LIVE: UFC Fight Night: Thompson vs Holland
programme.desc: Prelims - In the midst of a run up the welterweight ladder after an impressive middleweight run, Kevin “Trailblazer” Holland continues his crowd pleasing march to the top on December 3rd as he faces perennial contender Stephen “Wonderboy” Thompson in the five-round main event of UFC Fight Night at Amway Center in Orlando. Making his debut in the Sunshine State, South Carolina’s Thompson is one of the elite strikers in the UFC, but that’s just the kind of fight Texas’ Holland craves, setting the stage for a memorable night in the Octagon’s return to Florida. Plus, top five heavyweights go head-to-head as Australian knockout artist Tai Tuivasa looks to stop the surging Sergei Pavlovich, who is riding the momentum of four straight victories in the Octagon
